I like Tama's answers.

3919
03:24:29.400 --> 03:24:32.360
Well, thank you. That was unexpected, and I do want to thank you

3920
03:24:33.420 --> 03:24:35.280
for that honor, Minister,

3921
03:24:36.240 --> 03:24:39.700
Willie, Chair, and all of you. This has

3922
