quite trite when someone is leaving, but it has been an honor.

3924
03:24:47.870 --> 03:24:50.180
It has been difficult and some

3925
03:24:52.080 --> 03:24:56.060
of the issues that we've dealt with over the years, I mean, the period has

3926
03:24:56.100 --> 03:24:59.640
been beset with crises, but we've gone through that together,

3927
03:25:00.220 --> 03:25:03.840
and I do appreciate your support. And I know that support will

3928
03:25:03.880 --> 03:25:07.760
continue for my successor, Dion Tuuta, who is a

3929
03:25:07.800 --> 03:25:08.940
good man and

3930
03:25:09.840 --> 03:25:12.660
a very good senior level executive.

3931
03:25:13.360 --> 03:25:15.860
I remember when I came into the public service, I'd done,

3932
03:25:17.540 --> 03:25:21.490
I think it was 26 years of service in the military, and

3933
03:25:22.100 --> 03:25:25.440
now I've done a further 22 years of service in the public service.

3934
03:25:26.120 --> 03:25:27.800
When I came in, I was

3935
03:25:28.620 --> 03:25:32.420
brought into the public service by Charlie Tafia, who's now an

3936
03:25:32.580 --> 03:25:36.400
iwi leader in Tauranga. And we went to our first ministers

3937
03:25:36.480 --> 03:25:37.860
meeting, and it was

3938
03:25:41.120 --> 03:25:45.040
a bit of a shock for me. There were some strong words said, not at me in

3939
03:25:45.110 --> 03:25:47.819
particular, but we were a group of officials there.

3940
03:25:48.240 --> 03:25:50.300
And in the end, I walked out of that meeting

3941
03:25:51.400 --> 03:25:52.240
and looked at Charlie,

3942
03:25:53.220 --> 03:25:55.060
my senior, and just said,

3943
03:25:55.880 --> 03:25:59.620
"Jesus, is it always like that?" And he said, "Boy, welcome to the public

3944
03:25:59.700 --> 03:26:02.860
service. In your other profession, you could only get shot."

3945
03:26:04.150 --> 03:26:04.650
So kia ora tatou.

3946
03:26:06.120 --> 03:26:07.860
Unuhia, unuhia, unuhia e Turutapu.

3947
03:26:07.890 --> 03:26:11.580
Unuhia ki a mama, kia wātea, kia ngāwari hoki te wairua, te ngākau, te

3948
03:26:11.620 --> 03:26:15.500
