3949
03:26:15.520 --> 03:26:16.300
Tina.

3950
03:26:16.320 --> 03:26:16.960
Hui e.

3951
03:26:17.100 --> 03:26:19.220
Tāiki e. Ngā hua o Tina.

3952
03:26:20.300 --> 03:26:20.520
Kia ora.
